meanings: a great war, a world war, a major war
(궁전) a royal palace, a king's palace
(맞서 싸움) waging war, engagement, (상대하여 겨룸) competition, a match, a bout, 대전하다 oppose[confront, encounter] (the enemy), play ((a match)) against, have a game with, compete (with), fight (with)
(의식) a great function, a state ceremony
(법전) a code, a statute, a canon
